parameters:
Haruto: So, you know what happened? Chi-kun ate
bread all at once and then drank milk, and he went
like 'Buhh!!'
Hehe, Chihiro-kun is such a scatterbrain.

Haruto: So, you know what happened? Chi-kun ate
bread all at once and then drank milk, and he went
like 'Buhh!!'
S-Sorry, Haru-kun... Just wait a moment.

Hello... Shun-kun, what's up... \. Huh? Right now?
\. ...You said you were hungry and wanted me to
teach you an easy way to cook, didn't you?

...You want to eat my food...? \.Ugh... Well, I
guess there's no helping it. Just wait, I'll go
right away.

Sorry, Haru-kun. I have something to take care of,
so Mama will be going out for a bit.

Haruto: I understand! Mama, you've been busy
lately! Do your best!

Eh, th-thank you... I'll be back before dinner, so
please wait for me...
Haruto: Yeah! Have a safe trip!

(I'm sorry... Haru-kun... I'll make a delicious
dinner...)
